 the Minehunting PDS was procured via a sole source delivery order on the Raytheon IDIQ contract. A competitive production contract was awarded for future Minehunting PDS procurements in Q1 FY2025. The
 Mine Neutralization (MN) module will consist of the MCM USV with a near-surface mine neutralization payload, necessitating future procurement of MN PDSs.

